He was getting more and more pale, shaking his hands.

12:23.000 --> 12:27.000
Indeed, there are no traces of the contract in the accounting department,

12:27.000 --> 12:32.000
the director, Lekhadeev, or Varynokh.

12:32.000 --> 12:38.000
The accounting rules are that there are no documents, no circulation.

12:38.000 --> 12:44.000
The fact that there is a reflection of the economic operation in the accounting and tax records is present.

12:44.000 --> 12:49.000
However, the primary documents and economic contracts are either absent at all,

