or presented in dubious copies, or incomplete.

12:53.000 --> 13:01.000
This is exactly the typical mistake that leads to negative financial and tax consequences.

13:01.000 --> 13:09.000
There is a situation when the head of the organization does not agree with the opinion of the chief accountant.

13:09.000 --> 13:12.000
How to deal with this situation?

13:12.000 --> 13:17.000
In the event of a disagreement between the head of the organization and the chief accountant

13:17.000 --> 13:19.000
on the implementation of separate economic operations,

13:19.000 --> 13:28.000
the primary accounting documents can be used to carry out the written order of the head of the organization.

13:29.000 --> 13:34.000
Since the head of the organization bears full responsibility for the consequences of such operations

13:34.000 --> 13:38.000
and for including them in the accounting records.

13:38.000 --> 13:46.000
If the head of the organization has given the order, the accountant is obliged to include these documents in the accounting records.

13:46.000 --> 13:51.000
If the controlling authorities make a request for the removal of the primary documents,

13:52.000 --> 14:00.000
I would like to remind you that the accounting documents can be withdrawn only by the authorities of the preliminary investigation

14:00.000 --> 14:09.000
and the prosecutor's office, courts, and the Tax Administration on the basis of their decisions in accordance with the legislation of the Russian Federation.

14:09.000 --> 14:16.000
Do not forget that the decision on the withdrawal should contain a clear list of the documents and the reason for their withdrawal.

14:16.000 --> 14:21.000
The withdrawal of documents simply for verification by the current legislation is not provided.

14:21.000 --> 14:29.000
The chief accountant or another official of the organization has the right to remove copies of the documents

14:29.000 --> 14:37.000
with the indication of the basis and date of withdrawal from the permission of the representatives of the bodies carrying out the withdrawal.

14:38.000 --> 14:50.000
The forms of the primary documents that are taken into account by the accountants are developed and approved by the statistical bodies.

14:50.000 --> 15:03.000
At the moment, there are quite a lot of such forms, even in terms of their uniformity classification.

15:03.000 --> 15:10.000
For example, there are forms for accounting personnel, working hours and payroll,

15:10.000 --> 15:16.000
capital construction, products, commodity values,

15:16.000 --> 15:22.000
cash payments to the population with the use of cash machines,

15:22.000 --> 15:26.000
trading and cash transactions, inventory results,

15:26.000 --> 15:33.000
accounting for the main funds, non-material assets, accounting for materials, accounting for work in automotive, and so on.

15:33.000 --> 15:44.000
Many of them are obtained by the accountant after these documents pass through the hands of the manager or an ordinary employee of the organization.

15:44.000 --> 15:51.000
What requisites must be in these documents?

15:52.000 --> 16:01.000
The naming of the document is a financial and economic content of the economic operation.

16:01.000 --> 16:10.000
A document without a naming and a document with an unclear, poorly read naming has no legal power.

16:10.000 --> 16:20.000
The accountant must understand what document he is working with to decide on the economic operation that he should register in the accounting record.

16:20.000 --> 16:35.000
Often, the name of the document must include payment, tax, registration and mail requisites of legal and physical parties involved in the economic operation.

16:35.000 --> 16:45.000
A document without the naming of the requisites of at least one of the parties of the operation loses its addressability and cannot be accepted for execution.

16:45.000 --> 16:57.000
A document with an unclear writing or a document with no date loses its time period in which it should be registered.

16:57.000 --> 17:02.000
In fact, such a document also has no legal power.

17:02.000 --> 17:13.000
A document with a naming of the document in which it is reflected in its general form is also a necessary requisite for the maintenance of the economic operation.

17:13.000 --> 17:26.000
The necessity of a strict compliance with the naming of the document in the maintenance of the economic operation is determined by the principle of objectivity of registration in the accounting record.

17:26.000 --> 17:31.000
The document must contain measurements of the economic operation.

17:31.000 --> 17:39.000
The absence of a measurement in the document can be natural in terms of units of weight, size, labor, man-hour and money.

17:39.000 --> 17:49.000
According to the Russian Federation law, the absence of a measurement in the document in rubles deprives it of its accounting basis.

17:49.000 --> 18:05.000
If you have to work with commodity values that have a measurement in money, but in the money of other countries,

18:05.000 --> 18:17.000
it is allowed to add another count to this document, in which the conditional units or money units of other countries will be recalculated to the unit of Russia's accounting in rubles.

18:17.000 --> 18:24.000
The document must contain signatures of the responsible persons with the decryption of their positions and surnames.

18:24.000 --> 18:36.000
The first signature should belong to the head of the organization, the director of loans, for example, the general director, and the second signature should belong to the chief accountant.

18:36.000 --> 18:47.000
The required requisites for the primary document are the names of the documents, the names of the requisites of the parties, the date of the composition,

18:47.000 --> 18:55.000
the content of the economic operation, the measurements of the economic operation, and the signatures of the responsible persons.

18:55.000 --> 19:10.000
Disobedience to any of the requirements for the documentation can cause the workers of the controlling bodies to doubt the authenticity of the document presented to them,

19:10.000 --> 19:23.000
as a result of which the cost of the produced product and the dispute over the correctness of the profit calculation may be excluded.

19:23.000 --> 19:32.000
Thus, for example, in the absence of documents confirming the fact of the use of certain resources in the production process,

19:32.000 --> 19:41.000
when a document is checked, the workers of the tax authorities may deem it unlawful to deduct the costs for the cost of the product.

19:41.000 --> 19:46.000
There may be other negative consequences of incorrect documentation.

19:46.000 --> 20:00.000
For example, let's look at the situation. The salary of the workers for the production of parts was produced on the basis of the orders, which were not signed by the master or the head of the workshop.

20:00.000 --> 20:14.000
The absence of the signature of the responsible person on the orders for the production of works can mean both that such works were not produced at all, and that the works were actually produced, but they were not necessary.

20:14.000 --> 20:31.000
In the first case, we have the fact of the fraud of documents and the fact of money laundering, if the worker has already received a salary without a basis, as well as a reduction in the cost of living.

20:31.000 --> 20:39.000
In the second case, we have the fact of the irrational use of the enterprise funds and the reduction in the cost of living.

20:39.000 --> 20:48.000
In this case, the organization will have to look for other ways to prove the actual implementation of the costs and their production direction.

20:48.000 --> 20:57.000
One of the evidences may be documents confirming the delivery of the finished parts to the warehouse.

20:57.000 --> 21:09.000
However, in order to prove that the parts made according to the incorrectly designed orders were delivered to the warehouse, it will be necessary to analyze all the documents in the organization,

21:09.000 --> 21:15.000
the movement of materials and finished products, and to make inventory in the warehouse.

21:15.000 --> 21:21.000
As you can see, obtaining evidence is possible, but it is quite laborious.

21:21.000 --> 21:30.000
And when there are a lot of incorrectly designed documents in the account, it is difficult to implement them.

21:30.000 --> 21:38.000
The next situation is the one in the overhead. There is no date for obtaining the materials from the warehouse.

21:38.000 --> 21:47.000
The absence of a date for obtaining the materials from the warehouse does not allow us to determine the reporting period for the obtained materials.

21:47.000 --> 21:57.000
To determine this, we will have to make inventory of the materials and products made with their use,

21:57.000 --> 22:05.000
to conduct a comparative analysis of the movement of materials, the period of use in production and the delivery to the warehouse of the finished product,

22:05.000 --> 22:14.000
and to compare the obtained data with the data on the implementation of the finished product.

22:14.000 --> 22:21.000
The terms of the initial registration of the documents must be completed at the time of the economic operation.

22:21.000 --> 22:28.000
If this is not possible for objective reasons, then it must be done immediately after the operation.

22:28.000 --> 22:37.000
This is due to the fact that the main purpose of the initial registration of documents is to record the fact of the economic operation.

22:37.000 --> 22:42.000
In order to ensure that the document turnover is not overloaded, according to Russian legislation,

22:42.000 --> 22:50.000
the organization can modify the recommended typical forms of documents, taking into account the specifics of its activities.

22:50.000 --> 22:55.000
For example, add additional requisites.

22:55.000 --> 23:09.000
The organization issues cash reports on the economic and operational expenses of the employees in terms of size and term determined by the head.

23:09.000 --> 23:20.000
Those who receive cash reports are obliged to submit a document called an advance report to the accounting office

23:20.000 --> 23:27.000
within three working days after the deadline for which they are issued or upon return from a business trip.

23:27.000 --> 23:33.000
The report is about the spent amounts and the final calculation of them must be made.

23:33.000 --> 23:42.000
In practice, this happens often when an employee acquires material values for the employer's needs,

23:42.000 --> 23:49.000
not only without receiving the money report, but even without permission to act in the interests of the organization.

23:49.000 --> 23:59.000
Such permission to act in the interests of the organization gives the organization its trust.

23:59.000 --> 24:10.000
If the head does not have permission to issue an advance report, it turns out that the employee bought some property and then sold it to his home office.

24:10.000 --> 24:18.000
Therefore, when the employee is paid for his position, the payment of the property is not the expense of the transfer,

24:18.000 --> 24:27.000
but the payment of the property according to the purchase-sale contract and the physical receipt of the income.

24:28.000 --> 24:37.000
There is a limit to the amount of cash payments between legal entities and individuals.

24:37.000 --> 24:47.000
Today, this is 100,000 rubles per contract. This is the Bank of Russia's statement.

24:48.000 --> 25:01.000
There is an arbitration practice that indicates that only parties who bring cash from a superimposed limit should be held accountable for exceeding the limit.

25:01.000 --> 25:12.000
What to do if the initial document is issued, for example, the same deposit, and inaccuracies are made?

25:12.000 --> 25:15.000
What if a cash document is issued?

25:15.000 --> 25:20.000
The issuance of the correction is not allowed in cash and bank documents,

25:20.000 --> 25:31.000
and the correction can be made in other initial accounting documents based on the agreement with the parties who made and signed these documents.

25:31.000 --> 25:39.000
This must be confirmed by the signatures of the same parties with the date of the issuance of the correction.

25:39.000 --> 25:44.000
This can also be read in the textbook.

25:44.000 --> 25:48.000
Let's look at one example of the correction.

25:48.000 --> 25:58.000
The master of the sewing workshop, a financially responsible person, issued a demand for a deposit for the receipt of 120 satin-green shoulder straps from the warehouse.

25:58.000 --> 26:05.000
The head of the sewing workshop, signing the demand for a deposit, ordered to receive 150 meters of fabric.

26:06.000 --> 26:14.000
To correct the error, the master of the sewing workshop must mark the inscription 120, put 150 and write next to it,

