26:27.000 --> 26:37.000
Subsequently, other people who will sign this document, the head of the supply department, the warehouse keeper, should also put their signature under the correction record.

26:37.000 --> 26:47.000
Thus, if the correction is made at the initial stage of the composition of the document, it is better not to correct it, but to compose it again.

