27:11.000 --> 27:26.000
The list of persons who have the right to sign the primary accounting documents is approved by the head of the organization in accordance with the main accountant.

27:26.000 --> 27:39.000
The documents that are used to register an economic transaction with money are signed by the head of the organization, the main accountant, or the persons authorized to do so.

27:39.000 --> 27:53.000
Without the signature of the main accountant or the person authorized to do so, the financial and credit obligations of the money accounting documents are considered invalid and should not be executed.

27:53.000 --> 28:05.000
If a situation arises when a document is required to be signed by a person, but it is not specified in the list of persons who have the right to sign the corresponding documents,

28:05.000 --> 28:15.000
then the worker must be authorized by a special order of the head of the organization to carry out these actions.

28:15.000 --> 28:27.000
The order must include the visa of the main accountant, if the permission is granted to sign the money or accounting documents, as well as the financial or credit obligations.

28:27.000 --> 28:32.000
Or the worker must be given the appropriate confidentiality.

28:32.000 --> 28:41.000
If a document is signed by a person who does not belong to the organization, then the validity of such a document is controversial.

28:41.000 --> 28:52.000
Any party to the deal, as well as third parties to this basis, can insist that the validity of the document and the deal should be recognized.

28:53.000 --> 29:06.000
If the organization approves the actions of the workers, then the economic operation according to the Russian legislation is considered to be carried out on behalf of the organization.

29:06.000 --> 29:17.000
What will happen if the accounting documents are lost? Let's try to assess the extent of the disaster.

29:18.000 --> 29:24.000
There are different types of responsibility. Administrative and criminal.

29:24.000 --> 29:32.000
In what cases is the responsibility of the organization and its officials for the loss of accounting documents?

29:32.000 --> 29:38.000
The administrative penalty for the officials is the violation of the terms and order of storing documents.

29:38.000 --> 29:47.000
The official is the general director, accountant or person responsible for the preservation of documents.

29:47.000 --> 29:54.000
The administrative penalty can be as high as 2,000 to 3,000 rubles.

29:55.000 --> 30:11.000
The officials are also liable for the loss of accounting documents and tax authorities if these actions have caused a large or particularly large tax evasion.

